OL,3,COriginal sketches of Birmingham bronze
OL,4,Cbull fetch over #3,000 at auction
OL,6,FA portfolio of original sketches for
OL,7,Fthe designs of Birmingham's bronze
OL,8,Fbull have sold at an auction for more
OL,9,Fthan #3,000.
OL,11,FLaurence Broderick was the sculptor
OL,12,Fbehind the iconic structure that
OL,13,Fstands in the middle of the city
OL,14,Fcentre.
OL,16,FHe died at the age of 88 in April
OL,17,F2024, and with the drawings being
OL,18,Ffound at his address afterwards.
