OL,3,COriginal sketches of Birmingham bronze
OL,4,Cbull fetch over #3,000 at auction
OL,6,FThe lot comprising of 14 signed A2
OL,7,Fsketches, each dated July 2001 and
OL,8,Findividually numbered, was offered for
OL,9,Fsale by the family of the late Ingrid
OL,10,FChrista Broderick, the artist's wife.
OL,12,FIt also included 34 photographs of the
OL,13,Fmaquette, the smaller-scale model used
OL,14,Fin preparation for the full sculpture.
OL,16,FThe auction took place at Batemans
OL,17,FAuctioneers in Stamford in
OL,18,FLincolnshire.
