OL,3,COriginal sketches of Birmingham bronze
OL,4,Cbull fetch over #3,000 at auction
OL,6,FThe Broderick bull sketches sold for
OL,7,F#2,600 plus buyer's premium, which
OL,8,Ftotals #3,380 including premium.
